WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 6=

00:01:37.980 --> 00:01:39.650 line:80%
What's your connection to Qianmian Sect?

00:01:39.650 --> 00:01:41.130 line:80%
Who are you?

00:01:41.130 --> 00:01:42.900 line:80%
I'm Qian Xueshen,

00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:44.900 line:80%
the last descendant of Qianmian Sect.

00:01:45.090 --> 00:01:46.010 line:80%
Please understand.

00:01:46.420 --> 00:01:47.850 line:80%
They forced me to do this.

00:01:47.850 --> 00:01:49.490 line:80%
I'm just a scholar,

00:01:49.640 --> 00:01:50.570 line:80%
with elders and children

00:01:50.570 --> 00:01:51.410 line:80%
to care about.

00:02:00.980 --> 00:02:01.820 line:80%
The Demonic Camp.

00:02:22.020 --> 00:02:23.340 line:80%
Is this is the Chaos Needle?

00:02:24.370 --> 00:02:26.370 line:80%
The victim becomes weak and limp.

00:02:26.620 --> 00:02:28.313 line:80%
But the needle's aura
is extremely strong.

00:02:28.930 --> 00:02:30.210 line:80%
If it weren't someone familiar,

00:02:30.690 --> 00:02:32.180 line:80%
most would be on guard.

00:02:32.810 --> 00:02:33.970 line:80%
To silently take Xingjia away

00:02:34.060 --> 00:02:36.580 line:80%
from the sect shows

00:02:36.810 --> 00:02:38.250 line:80%
that the Demonic Camp's influence

00:02:39.620 --> 00:02:41.460 line:80%
has infiltrated the whole sect.

00:02:41.780 --> 00:02:43.690 line:80%
With Qianmian Sect's Body Shift,

00:02:44.620 --> 00:02:45.690 line:80%
it's not impossible.

00:02:46.130 --> 00:02:47.490 line:80%
The Qianmian Sect is so powerful?

00:02:48.020 --> 00:02:49.370 line:80%
Yet I've never heard of it before.

00:02:49.650 --> 00:02:50.690 line:80%
Long ago,

00:02:50.780 --> 00:02:53.020 line:80%
they were wiped out
by the righteous and demonic sects.

00:02:53.580 --> 00:02:55.090 line:80%
The Qianmian Sect's Body Shift

00:02:55.690 --> 00:02:58.250 line:80%
can alter a person's appearance,

00:02:58.860 --> 00:03:00.140 line:80%
leaving no trace.

00:03:00.530 --> 00:03:01.810 line:80%
Their last lord,

00:03:02.060 --> 00:03:02.970 line:80%
Qianmian Slayer,

00:03:03.410 --> 00:03:04.690 line:80%
used it to cause chaos

00:03:05.090 --> 00:03:06.683 line:80%
and was rejected by the righteous sects.

00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:09.026 line:80%
Later, he brought the sect
to join the demon sect.

00:03:09.180 --> 00:03:10.900 line:80%
But the demon sect exposed

00:03:10.900 --> 00:03:11.810 line:80%
their hideout,

00:03:12.340 --> 00:03:13.810 line:80%
drawing elites from the Six Sects;

00:03:14.410 --> 00:03:16.410 line:80%
thus, the sect was wiped out.

00:03:17.583 --> 00:03:18.860 line:80%
The alliance with the demon sect

00:03:19.530 --> 00:03:20.690 line:80%
was disgraceful,

00:03:21.823 --> 00:03:23.463 line:80%
so the righteous sects
did not record it,

00:03:23.580 --> 00:03:24.780 line:80%
which is why you wouldn't know.

00:03:27.060 --> 00:03:28.410 line:80%
If there are no records,

00:03:28.930 --> 00:03:30.580 line:80%
how did you know?

00:03:31.060 --> 00:03:31.900 line:80%
From Jiuzhou...

00:03:37.740 --> 00:03:38.930 line:80%
Jiuzhou Chronicles.

00:03:40.090 --> 00:03:40.930 line:80%
I never expected

00:03:42.220 --> 00:03:43.060 line:80%
there to be

00:03:43.060 --> 00:03:44.810 line:80%
a descendant of Qianmian Sect.

00:03:46.460 --> 00:03:47.300 line:80%
So,

00:03:47.930 --> 00:03:49.650 line:80%
does the Chronicles record

00:03:50.740 --> 00:03:52.900 line:80%
a way to counter this move?

00:03:53.416 --> 00:03:54.946 line:80%
That is an internal secret of the sect.

00:03:55.900 --> 00:03:56.740 line:80%
I think

00:03:57.180 --> 00:03:58.690 line:80%
only Qian Xueshen would know.

00:03:59.180 --> 00:04:00.340 line:80%
But with all this commotion,

00:04:00.780 --> 00:04:02.690 line:80%
they probably already moved him.

00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:07.580 line:80%
Chang?

00:04:07.930 --> 00:04:08.770 line:80%
Zhao?

00:04:11.140 --> 00:04:12.300 line:80%
Where are we?

00:04:12.490 --> 00:04:13.330 line:80%
Simply put,

00:04:13.650 --> 00:04:14.620 line:80%
you were kidnapped,

00:04:15.180 --> 00:04:16.020 line:80%
but we rescued you.

00:04:24.850 --> 00:04:26.380 line:80%
Why are there butterflies?

00:04:26.380 --> 00:04:28.410 line:80%
I sprinkled pollen on Qian Xueshen.

00:04:28.940 --> 00:04:29.780 line:80%
Let's go find him.

00:04:40.650 --> 00:04:42.580 line:80%
They actually entered Qingque Sect?

00:04:43.613 --> 00:04:45.600 line:80%
Isn't this like sheep walking
into a tiger's den?

00:04:45.850 --> 00:04:47.020 line:80%
Maybe they are the tigers,

00:04:47.850 --> 00:04:48.820 line:80%
and we are the sheep.

00:05:14.260 --> 00:05:15.100 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:15.210 --> 00:05:16.170 line:80%
I'll go ask around.

00:05:24.290 --> 00:05:25.580 line:80%
The Body Shift has been exposed.

00:05:26.650 --> 00:05:28.050 line:80%
The enemy will surely be on guard.

00:05:28.530 --> 00:05:29.530 line:80%
Returning to the sect now

00:05:29.780 --> 00:05:30.850 line:80%
would be extremely risky.

00:05:31.050 --> 00:05:31.900 line:80%
I know.

00:05:32.140 --> 00:05:33.700 line:80%
But Master's injuries have yet to heal.

00:05:33.900 --> 00:05:35.170 line:80%
I must warn him first.

00:05:36.290 --> 00:05:37.340 line:80%
The situation is perilous.

00:05:37.820 --> 00:05:38.970 line:80%
You should think it through

00:05:39.503 --> 00:05:41.230 line:80%
about whether you want
to risk your life.

00:05:43.530 --> 00:05:44.370 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:05:44.780 --> 00:05:46.020 line:80%
I can handle it myself.

00:05:46.560 --> 00:05:47.410 line:80%
Perhaps this will be

00:05:47.410 --> 00:05:48.250 line:80%
our last meeting.

00:05:48.850 --> 00:05:49.730 line:80%
Let's forget the past.

00:05:50.076 --> 00:05:51.130 line:80%
The martial world is vast.

00:05:51.410 --> 00:05:52.260 line:80%
Take care, Ning.

00:05:53.626 --> 00:05:55.730 line:80%
The lodging fees I owed you
haven't been settled yet.

00:05:56.886 --> 00:05:58.140 line:80%
After helping you one last time,

00:06:00.020 --> 00:06:01.050 line:80%
we'll be even.

00:06:04.730 --> 00:06:05.570 line:80%
Zhao.

00:06:08.120 --> 00:06:08.970 line:80%
What's going on?

00:06:08.970 --> 00:06:09.850 line:80%
The guards said

00:06:10.340 --> 00:06:12.290 line:80%
a few groups entered last night.

00:06:12.530 --> 00:06:13.370 line:80%
But

00:06:13.530 --> 00:06:14.940 line:80%
they all had orders from Master.

00:06:15.193 --> 00:06:16.460 line:80%
Who were those in gray just now?

00:06:16.500 --> 00:06:17.730 line:80%
They are the reinforcements

00:06:18.090 --> 00:06:19.290 line:80%
I mentioned before.

00:06:19.650 --> 00:06:20.610 line:80%
All Qingque lords

00:06:20.650 --> 00:06:22.290 line:80%
cultivate some martial artists

00:06:22.413 --> 00:06:23.500 line:80%
to call upon in emergencies.

00:06:23.850 --> 00:06:25.210 line:80%
They are commanded by the Lord;

00:06:25.210 --> 00:06:26.610 line:80%
even Uncle Li can't control them.

00:06:42.650 --> 00:06:43.490 line:80%
Milady.

00:06:43.850 --> 00:06:44.690 line:80%
Zhao,

00:06:45.090 --> 00:06:46.850 line:80%
I heard you searched for Fan all night.

00:06:46.970 --> 00:06:47.810 line:80%
Is everything okay?

00:06:48.090 --> 00:06:49.900 line:80%
(Weak inner energy. She's real.)

00:06:50.170 --> 00:06:51.010 line:80%
It's fine.

00:06:51.020 --> 00:06:51.970 line:80%
Just a little trouble.

00:06:52.460 --> 00:06:53.300 line:80%
It's all resolved.

00:06:56.260 --> 00:06:57.100 line:80%
Zhuo,

00:06:58.290 --> 00:07:00.020 line:80%
have you finished the Sober Powder

00:07:00.310 --> 00:07:01.160 line:80%
Feicui made for you?

00:07:01.170 --> 00:07:02.120 line:80%
It wasn't me.

00:07:03.340 --> 00:07:04.970 line:80%
It was your mother.

00:07:05.380 --> 00:07:06.220 line:80%
I've finished it.

00:07:06.500 --> 00:07:07.420 line:80%
Yeah, it was my mother.

00:07:07.900 --> 00:07:08.740 line:80%
That's good.

00:07:09.500 --> 00:07:10.340 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:07:10.510 --> 00:07:12.059 line:80%
why didn't you tell us before you left?

00:07:12.530 --> 00:07:13.610 line:80%
I wanted to,

00:07:13.780 --> 00:07:15.780 line:80%
but I was sleeping in my room.

00:07:15.970 --> 00:07:17.467 line:80%
I woke up and find myself in the town,

00:07:17.530 --> 00:07:18.730 line:80%
almost losing my life.

00:07:19.460 --> 00:07:20.530 line:80%
Someone took Xingjia away

00:07:20.730 --> 00:07:22.530 line:80%
without anyone noticing.

00:07:22.850 --> 00:07:23.900 line:80%
It means many intruders

00:07:25.020 --> 00:07:26.500 line:80%
must have infiltrated the sect.

00:07:35.820 --> 00:07:36.780 line:80%
Master is in seclusion.

00:07:37.410 --> 00:07:38.380 line:80%
No one may see him

00:07:39.410 --> 00:07:40.250 line:80%
except for Dalou.

00:07:41.530 --> 00:07:42.780 line:80%
Why not talk to Uncle Li?

00:07:43.290 --> 00:07:44.500 line:80%
I just went to the kitchen

00:07:44.820 --> 00:07:46.416 line:80%
and saw Uncle Li Wenxun

00:07:46.427 --> 00:07:47.610 line:80%
talking to some guards in gray

00:07:47.610 --> 00:07:48.850 line:80%
whom I've never seen.

00:07:49.290 --> 00:07:51.580 line:80%
He even told the cooks
to take care of them.

00:07:58.210 --> 00:07:59.580 line:80%
It's best not to alert anyone yet.

00:08:02.610 --> 00:08:03.450 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:08:03.820 --> 00:08:05.410 line:80%
check around with Zhuo.

00:08:06.050 --> 00:08:07.290 line:80%
Look for suspicious people.

00:08:09.140 --> 00:08:09.980 line:80%
Ning,

00:08:10.940 --> 00:08:12.820 line:80%
go find Qian Xueshen with Xingjia.

00:08:13.500 --> 00:08:14.340 line:80%
What about you?

00:08:15.700 --> 00:08:16.580 line:80%
Master will see me.

00:08:25.506 --> 00:08:26.730 line:80%
The Lord is in seclusion today,

00:08:27.050 --> 00:08:27.890 line:80%
not seeing anyone.

00:08:31.380 --> 00:08:32.530 line:80%
Please tell Master

00:08:33.220 --> 00:08:34.500 line:80%
that I have an urgent matter.

00:08:34.690 --> 00:08:35.710 line:80%
The Lord won't see anyone.

00:08:35.930 --> 00:08:36.682 line:80%
Did you hear that?

00:08:36.693 --> 00:08:38.375 line:80%
My father said
he doesn't want to see you.

00:08:38.386 --> 00:08:38.980 line:80%
Leave.

00:08:39.913 --> 00:08:41.170 line:80%
The Lord is in seclusion today,

00:08:41.380 --> 00:08:42.220 line:80%
not seeing anyone.

00:08:42.740 --> 00:08:44.900 line:80%
I brought soup to my father.

00:08:45.020 --> 00:08:46.550 line:80%
He will see me. Let me through.

00:08:46.570 --> 00:08:47.620 line:80%
The Lord won't see anyone.

00:08:49.690 --> 00:08:50.530 line:80%
Forget it, Lingbo.

00:08:51.140 --> 00:08:52.330 line:80%
I suppose these two

00:08:52.330 --> 00:08:53.530 line:80%
are acting on Master's orders.

00:08:54.170 --> 00:08:55.170 line:80%
It seems Master

00:08:55.740 --> 00:08:56.693 line:80%
doesn't want to see you.

00:08:57.336 --> 00:08:58.410 line:80%
What does it matter to you?

00:09:01.410 --> 00:09:02.500 line:80%
It's a pity

00:09:02.780 --> 00:09:04.330 line:80%
no one will drink the soup

00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:06.860 line:80%
you carefully prepared.

00:09:10.330 --> 00:09:11.810 line:80%
I'll go in today.

00:09:11.810 --> 00:09:12.650 line:80%
Let me through.

00:09:12.780 --> 00:09:13.620 line:80%
Miss Qi.

00:09:16.530 --> 00:09:17.650 line:80%
You two!

00:09:17.780 --> 00:09:18.483 line:80%
How could you?

00:09:18.494 --> 00:09:19.690 line:80%
Give me back my chicken soup!

00:09:19.690 --> 00:09:20.860 line:80%
My chicken soup!

00:09:20.860 --> 00:09:21.860 line:80%
Give it back!

00:09:22.220 --> 00:09:23.100 line:80%
My chicken soup!

00:09:23.100 --> 00:09:24.209 line:80%
How dare you touch

00:09:24.220 --> 00:09:25.980 line:80%
- my chicken soup?
- It's the Lord's order.

00:09:31.810 --> 00:09:32.650 line:80%
Zhao.

00:09:33.260 --> 00:09:34.860 line:80%
Master, are you alright?

00:09:34.900 --> 00:09:35.740 line:80%
Don't come closer.

00:09:37.260 --> 00:09:38.260 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:09:40.170 --> 00:09:42.450 line:80%
Did you come for something urgent?

00:09:42.780 --> 00:09:43.690 line:80%
Last night, Xingjia

00:09:44.260 --> 00:09:46.260 line:80%
was taken away by the Demonic Camp.

00:09:46.980 --> 00:09:47.820 line:80%
Understood.

00:09:49.410 --> 00:09:50.500 line:80%
Dalou, let me through.

00:09:50.500 --> 00:09:51.340 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:09:51.450 --> 00:09:52.290 line:80%
you can't enter.

00:09:52.740 --> 00:09:54.020 line:80%
When did you come in?

00:09:54.650 --> 00:09:55.490 line:80%
While you

00:09:55.679 --> 00:09:56.873 line:80%
were killing your way through.

00:09:57.140 --> 00:09:58.260 line:80%
You used me!

00:09:59.500 --> 00:10:00.340 line:80%
Father,

00:10:00.636 --> 00:10:01.530 line:80%
she caused me to spill

00:10:01.860 --> 00:10:03.860 line:80%
the chicken soup I made for you.

00:10:03.989 --> 00:10:05.090 line:80%
She even provoked me to act.

00:10:05.140 --> 00:10:06.020 line:80%
Who let you come here?

00:10:06.780 --> 00:10:07.620 line:80%
Everyone, out.

00:10:07.930 --> 00:10:08.860 line:80%
Father.

00:10:09.260 --> 00:10:10.100 line:80%
Yunke,

00:10:10.410 --> 00:10:12.900 line:80%
are you kicking me out, too?

00:10:13.140 --> 00:10:13.980 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:10:14.260 --> 00:10:15.810 line:80%
Master is recovering from injury.

00:10:15.821 --> 00:10:17.179 line:80%
It's not the time to be distracted.

00:10:17.190 --> 00:10:18.020 line:80%
Please leave.

00:10:18.570 --> 00:10:19.410 line:80%
Father,

00:10:21.050 --> 00:10:22.690 line:80%
you've been in seclusion
for a long time.

00:10:22.740 --> 00:10:24.050 line:80%
You haven't seen Mother and Yuzhi

00:10:24.140 --> 00:10:25.630 line:80%
- for so long.
- Lingbo.

00:10:25.650 --> 00:10:26.520 line:80%
Shut up!

00:10:26.520 --> 00:10:27.370 line:80%
Zeng Dalou!

00:10:36.900 --> 00:10:37.740 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:10:38.260 --> 00:10:39.930 line:80%
Master's poisoning injury is severe.

00:10:40.223 --> 00:10:41.243 line:80%
It can't be taken lightly.

00:10:41.410 --> 00:10:42.780 line:80%
Please understand.

00:10:46.500 --> 00:10:47.340 line:80%
Yunke,

00:10:48.620 --> 00:10:49.460 line:80%
I'm your wife.

00:10:50.100 --> 00:10:51.380 line:80%
If something is wrong,

00:10:51.980 --> 00:10:53.100 line:80%
you should tell me.

00:10:53.380 --> 00:10:54.220 line:80%
Dear,

00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:55.650 line:80%
don't worry.

00:10:56.780 --> 00:10:58.220 line:80%
When my injuries heal,

00:10:58.650 --> 00:10:59.570 line:80%
I'll go see you.

00:11:00.690 --> 00:11:01.980 line:80%
You all should leave first.

00:11:06.690 --> 00:11:07.530 line:80%
Mother.

00:11:08.690 --> 00:11:10.150 line:80%
- Mother.
- Master,

00:11:10.170 --> 00:11:11.010 line:80%
I take my leave.

00:11:12.980 --> 00:11:13.820 line:80%
Master,

00:11:14.290 --> 00:11:16.050 line:80%
I'll leave first.

00:11:16.570 --> 00:11:17.410 line:80%
Sure.

00:11:25.100 --> 00:11:25.940 line:80%
Master,

00:11:26.436 --> 00:11:27.690 line:80%
this is a glazed lantern, right?

00:11:28.380 --> 00:11:30.290 line:80%
You gave me one when I was nine.

00:11:30.530 --> 00:11:31.410 line:80%
I liked it very much.

00:11:31.570 --> 00:11:32.620 line:80%
If you like it,

00:11:33.100 --> 00:11:33.980 line:80%
take it.

00:11:35.380 --> 00:11:36.690 line:80%
Now, it makes a pair.

00:11:39.050 --> 00:11:39.930 line:80%
Thank you, Master.

00:11:44.740 --> 00:11:45.930 line:80%
You're really kind to me.

00:11:55.980 --> 00:11:56.820 line:80%
What?

00:11:56.930 --> 00:11:58.330 line:80%
Master is fake, too?

00:11:59.050 --> 00:11:59.890 line:80%
Lower your voice.

00:12:00.450 --> 00:12:01.290 line:80%
What?

00:12:01.500 --> 00:12:02.860 line:80%
Master is fake, too?

00:12:02.860 --> 00:12:03.700 line:80%
When I was nine,

00:12:03.731 --> 00:12:05.659 line:80%
the path in Luoying Valley
was slippery in snow.

00:12:05.690 --> 00:12:06.650 line:80%
Master fell,

00:12:07.020 --> 00:12:08.170 line:80%
and the lantern broke.

00:12:09.260 --> 00:12:11.020 line:80%
Master blamed himself for a long time.

00:12:11.330 --> 00:12:12.260 line:80%
If Master were real,

00:12:13.410 --> 00:12:14.410 line:80%
he'd know the lantern

00:12:14.410 --> 00:12:15.900 line:80%
can't make a pair again.

00:12:18.330 --> 00:12:19.170 line:80%
Zhuo,

00:12:20.186 --> 00:12:21.546 line:80%
have you noticed anyone suspicious?

00:12:21.740 --> 00:12:22.833 line:80%
Besides the people in gray,

00:12:24.050 --> 00:12:24.890 line:80%
there's no evidence.

00:12:26.533 --> 00:12:27.460 line:80%
What about you, Xingjia?

00:12:27.530 --> 00:12:28.780 line:80%
Any clue about Qian Xueshen?

00:12:29.450 --> 00:12:30.559 line:80%
I searched the water prison,

00:12:30.570 --> 00:12:32.100 line:80%
dungeon, dry prison,

00:12:32.111 --> 00:12:33.010 line:80%
and the back storeroom

00:12:33.050 --> 00:12:35.140 line:80%
of the Disciples' Dorm.

00:12:35.220 --> 00:12:36.060 line:80%
No one at all.

00:12:36.650 --> 00:12:38.930 line:80%
Could it be
the Trace Butterfly misled us?

00:12:40.220 --> 00:12:41.060 line:80%
I don't think so.

00:12:44.260 --> 00:12:46.170 line:80%
Ning, you know the sect well.

00:12:47.290 --> 00:12:48.140 line:80%
Do you know

00:12:48.810 --> 00:12:50.030 line:80%
where else someone could hide?

00:12:53.900 --> 00:12:55.170 line:80%
I heard Lord Yin Dai

00:12:56.530 --> 00:12:57.810 line:80%
built a secret prison.

00:12:58.290 --> 00:13:00.380 line:80%
It's extremely hidden.

00:13:00.650 --> 00:13:01.690 line:80%
Only a few know.

00:13:02.220 --> 00:13:03.060 line:80%
Unless...

00:13:13.410 --> 00:13:14.330 line:80%
Thanks, Yuzhi.

00:13:16.810 --> 00:13:18.690 line:80%
I know you are severely injured

00:13:18.690 --> 00:13:19.970 line:80%
and must be on guard constantly.

00:13:20.450 --> 00:13:21.640 line:80%
But isn't it

00:13:22.220 --> 00:13:23.380 line:80%
a bit excessive?

00:13:26.620 --> 00:13:27.460 line:80%
Uncle Pang.

00:13:27.460 --> 00:13:28.700 line:80%
(Pang Xiongxin, Guangtian Sect)

00:13:40.020 --> 00:13:41.500 line:80%
You act like facing a great enemy.

00:13:42.140 --> 00:13:44.260 line:80%
Do you find something off?

00:13:50.620 --> 00:13:52.740 line:80%
Xingjia was almost switched yesterday.

00:13:53.050 --> 00:13:55.570 line:80%
I hope you'll be honest with me.

00:14:00.860 --> 00:14:01.930 line:80%
Lately, Master

00:14:02.530 --> 00:14:03.570 line:80%
hasn't visited me

00:14:04.140 --> 00:14:05.500 line:80%
or met Lady Yin.

00:14:06.100 --> 00:14:07.650 line:80%
Master always doted on Lady Yin.

00:14:07.930 --> 00:14:09.740 line:80%
No matter how she angered him before,

00:14:10.050 --> 00:14:11.810 line:80%
he would never be so heartless.

00:14:12.620 --> 00:14:13.500 line:80%
As expected.

00:14:14.690 --> 00:14:15.530 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:14:17.260 --> 00:14:18.290 line:80%
have you heard

00:14:19.290 --> 00:14:20.900 line:80%
of the Body Shift?

00:14:24.220 --> 00:14:25.060 line:80%
Chang!

00:14:29.223 --> 00:14:30.323 line:80%
She's been gone for so long.

00:14:30.650 --> 00:14:31.810 line:80%
If Song Yuzhi is fake,

00:14:32.450 --> 00:14:33.450 line:80%
Zhao could be in danger.

00:14:33.620 --> 00:14:35.220 line:80%
Yuzhi was poisoned by Nether Aura.

00:14:35.260 --> 00:14:36.260 line:80%
The aura can't be faked.

00:14:36.980 --> 00:14:38.690 line:80%
See? You're just too worried.

00:14:39.020 --> 00:14:39.860 line:80%
Let's wait a bit.

00:14:41.980 --> 00:14:42.820 line:80%
Chang.

00:14:43.530 --> 00:14:44.370 line:80%
Chang!

00:14:44.860 --> 00:14:46.780 line:80%
I always felt this sect attack

00:14:46.780 --> 00:14:47.650 line:80%
was strange.

00:14:49.570 --> 00:14:50.570 line:80%
So, they aimed at Master

00:14:50.570 --> 00:14:51.690 line:80%
from the start.

00:14:53.690 --> 00:14:55.009 line:80%
Master's martial power is supreme.

00:14:55.020 --> 00:14:55.860 line:80%
He's hard to imitate.

00:14:56.260 --> 00:14:58.330 line:80%
The only way the impostor

00:14:58.740 --> 00:14:59.740 line:80%
could avoid detection

00:15:00.620 --> 00:15:01.570 line:80%
is to go into seclusion.

00:15:02.213 --> 00:15:03.220 line:80%
Where is the real Master?

00:15:03.220 --> 00:15:04.450 line:80%
Master is a lord.

00:15:04.810 --> 00:15:06.023 line:80%
For such an important hostage,

00:15:06.380 --> 00:15:08.140 line:80%
until they achieve their goal,

00:15:08.290 --> 00:15:09.500 line:80%
they will keep him alive.

00:15:13.020 --> 00:15:14.330 line:80%
We must not act rashly,

00:15:15.050 --> 00:15:16.930 line:80%
lest they panic and kill
to cover their tracks.

00:15:17.330 --> 00:15:18.860 line:80%
We should first find Qian Xueshen

00:15:18.860 --> 00:15:20.273 line:80%
and ask about Master's whereabouts.

00:15:20.450 --> 00:15:21.290 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:15:21.900 --> 00:15:23.740 line:80%
do you know if there's a secret prison

00:15:24.740 --> 00:15:25.810 line:80%
in Qingque Sect?

00:15:26.980 --> 00:15:27.820 line:80%
Secret prison?

00:15:29.500 --> 00:15:31.140 line:80%
My grandfather did have one.

00:15:32.720 --> 00:15:33.570 line:80%
This secret prison

00:15:33.570 --> 00:15:35.410 line:80%
was where Elder Kaiyang was held.

00:15:35.650 --> 00:15:36.810 line:80%
It's under the Library,

00:15:37.140 --> 00:15:37.980 line:80%
but now abandoned.

00:15:45.140 --> 00:15:45.980 line:80%
Let's go.

00:15:48.450 --> 00:15:49.690 line:80%
Yuzhi, with your injuries,

00:15:49.900 --> 00:15:51.330 line:80%
you should stay here and keep watch.

00:15:51.930 --> 00:15:52.770 line:80%
I'm going.

00:15:52.900 --> 00:15:53.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:15:54.196 --> 00:15:56.710 line:80%
the secret prison is dangerous
after being abandoned for years.

00:15:56.780 --> 00:15:58.170 line:80%
I must go with you.

00:15:59.860 --> 00:16:01.630 line:80%
You're so weak.

00:16:01.810 --> 00:16:02.900 line:80%
What good will that do?

00:16:04.740 --> 00:16:06.810 line:80%
Not everything relies on brute force.

00:16:12.780 --> 00:16:13.860 line:80%
Both of you, stop arguing.

00:16:14.260 --> 00:16:15.500 line:80%
Zhao is going down.

00:16:16.450 --> 00:16:17.620 line:80%
I'll stay and keep watch.

00:16:34.100 --> 00:16:36.146 line:80%
Back then, Lu Chengnan,
Leader of the Demonic Camp,

00:16:36.260 --> 00:16:37.410 line:80%
once infiltrated Qingque Sect

00:16:37.410 --> 00:16:38.810 line:80%
and tried to seize Elder Kaiyang.

00:16:39.100 --> 00:16:41.570 line:80%
Surely, there was a fierce battle here.

00:16:41.860 --> 00:16:44.290 line:80%
Lord Yin hid Elder Kaiyang deeply.

00:16:44.410 --> 00:16:45.930 line:80%
It seems he's determined

00:16:46.020 --> 00:16:46.893 line:80%
to get what he wanted.

00:16:46.980 --> 00:16:48.200 line:80%
The demon sect acted cunningly.

00:16:48.290 --> 00:16:49.860 line:80%
My grandfather was to prevent trouble.

00:16:57.140 --> 00:16:58.410 line:80%
Are you two here to argue,

00:16:58.410 --> 00:16:59.260 line:80%
or to help?

00:17:03.260 --> 00:17:04.100 line:80%
In a critical moment,

00:17:04.570 --> 00:17:05.670 line:80%
won't brute force be needed?

00:17:13.090 --> 00:17:16.020 line:80%
Don't kill me!

00:17:17.940 --> 00:17:18.780 line:80%
It's me.

00:17:19.780 --> 00:17:20.620 line:80%
It's you.

00:17:20.850 --> 00:17:21.780 line:80%
How did you find me?

00:17:21.780 --> 00:17:22.620 line:80%
Enough talk.

00:17:27.946 --> 00:17:29.130 line:80%
Song, don't waste your effort.

00:17:29.270 --> 00:17:31.020 line:80%
These iron chains
likely contain black iron.

00:17:31.020 --> 00:17:32.460 line:80%
Normal weapons can't cut them.

00:17:33.500 --> 00:17:34.340 line:80%
I think

00:17:34.799 --> 00:17:36.135 line:80%
we should just chop off his hands.

00:17:36.220 --> 00:17:37.460 line:80%
No! Spare me, please!

00:17:37.460 --> 00:17:39.130 line:80%
I was also captured.

00:17:39.180 --> 00:17:40.420 line:80%
It's not my fault!

00:17:42.290 --> 00:17:43.503 line:80%
Among the people you disguised,

00:17:43.740 --> 00:17:45.460 line:80%
was there a Qingque Lord?

00:17:45.460 --> 00:17:47.260 line:80%
I never leave my house.

00:17:47.500 --> 00:17:49.370 line:80%
How would I know who the Lord is?

00:17:49.530 --> 00:17:50.460 line:80%
Around 40 years old,

00:17:51.020 --> 00:17:51.860 line:80%
handsome,

00:17:52.180 --> 00:17:53.020 line:80%
with a beard.

00:17:53.050 --> 00:17:53.890 line:80%
He might be poisoned

00:17:53.946 --> 00:17:54.992 line:80%
but has deep internal power

00:17:55.050 --> 00:17:56.003 line:80%
and strange meridians,

00:17:56.180 --> 00:17:57.260 line:80%
beyond ordinary people.

00:17:57.610 --> 00:17:59.180 line:80%
I think there is such a person.

00:18:01.020 --> 00:18:01.860 line:80%
Where is he?

00:18:02.660 --> 00:18:04.370 line:80%
I changed his face in Qingque Town;

00:18:05.050 --> 00:18:06.220 line:80%
then he was taken away.

00:18:06.220 --> 00:18:07.260 line:80%
I don't know where he went,

00:18:07.530 --> 00:18:09.420 line:80%
but anyone taken is important.

00:18:09.460 --> 00:18:10.780 line:80%
They usually don't hurry to kill.

00:18:10.890 --> 00:18:12.130 line:80%
How to counter the Body Shift?

00:18:13.810 --> 00:18:15.940 line:80%
My Body Shift

00:18:16.180 --> 00:18:17.180 line:80%
is exquisite.

00:18:17.370 --> 00:18:18.460 line:80%
There's no solution.

00:18:19.660 --> 00:18:20.610 line:80%
If so,

00:18:21.020 --> 00:18:21.890 line:80%
then you're useless.

00:18:22.460 --> 00:18:23.500 line:80%
I can help you.

00:18:23.660 --> 00:18:24.500 line:80%
There is a way!

00:18:24.660 --> 00:18:25.740 line:80%
Once the person dies,

00:18:26.370 --> 00:18:27.210 line:80%
the effect ends.

00:18:27.420 --> 00:18:29.420 line:80%
Saliva of the Snow-Scale Beast.

00:18:30.530 --> 00:18:31.530 line:80%
Snow-Scale Beast?

00:18:33.660 --> 00:18:34.500 line:80%
Where?

00:18:37.050 --> 00:18:38.530 line:80%
Head straight north

00:18:38.972 --> 00:18:40.791 line:80%
into the snow mountains
in the Freezing Area.

00:18:41.290 --> 00:18:42.940 line:80%
I've told you everything I know.

00:18:43.130 --> 00:18:44.130 line:80%
If you want to save him,

00:18:44.220 --> 00:18:45.290 line:80%
hurry to get the saliva.

00:18:45.530 --> 00:18:46.780 line:80%
Once the fake takes control,

00:18:47.500 --> 00:18:49.130 line:80%
the real one will be near death.

00:18:49.940 --> 00:18:50.810 line:80%
We'll get you out,

00:18:51.020 --> 00:18:52.093 line:80%
lest you harm anyone again.

00:18:55.786 --> 00:18:57.426 line:80%
This is the sect's alarm bell
for danger.

00:18:57.500 --> 00:18:58.400 line:80%
We've been discovered.

00:18:59.260 --> 00:18:59.813 line:80%
Good.

00:18:59.900 --> 00:19:01.729 line:80%
Let's take him out
and confront the impostor.

00:19:01.740 --> 00:19:04.130 line:80%
No, how can you claim
the Lord is fake

00:19:04.513 --> 00:19:05.660 line:80%
with an unknown Qian Xueshen?

00:19:05.660 --> 00:19:06.500 line:80%
It's the only way.

00:19:06.740 --> 00:19:07.580 line:80%
Breaking into here,

00:19:07.756 --> 00:19:09.090 line:80%
we can't handle it peacefully now.

00:19:09.460 --> 00:19:11.090 line:80%
Why not make a commotion?

00:19:11.260 --> 00:19:12.530 line:80%
This way,

00:19:12.740 --> 00:19:13.580 line:80%
they'll take notice,

00:19:13.890 --> 00:19:15.370 line:80%
and we can buy time for Master,

00:19:15.700 --> 00:19:16.680 line:80%
keeping him safe for now.

00:19:17.740 --> 00:19:18.580 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:19:18.740 --> 00:19:19.580 line:80%
you stay here.

00:19:19.600 --> 00:19:20.780 line:80%
If I can't get out,

00:19:20.940 --> 00:19:22.610 line:80%
you must go to retrieve the saliva

00:19:23.370 --> 00:19:24.210 line:80%
and save Master.

00:19:24.890 --> 00:19:25.730 line:80%
Understood.

00:19:25.980 --> 00:19:26.820 line:80%
Be careful.

00:19:27.370 --> 00:19:28.260 line:80%
No one will believe

00:19:28.260 --> 00:19:29.850 line:80%
the Lord of the top sect is fake.

00:19:31.180 --> 00:19:32.130 line:80%
No one will believe you.

00:19:34.980 --> 00:19:37.140 line:80%
(Dusk Palace)

00:19:37.610 --> 00:19:40.130 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
The demonic sect is attacking us.

00:19:41.370 --> 00:19:43.330 line:80%
I've been investigating.

00:19:43.570 --> 00:19:45.370 line:80%
And I've received news.

00:19:51.793 --> 00:19:53.032 line:80%
The demonic sect found someone

00:19:53.130 --> 00:19:55.370 line:80%
from Qianmian Sect.

00:19:56.890 --> 00:19:59.500 line:80%
To avoid a jailbreak
by the demonic sect,

00:20:00.290 --> 00:20:02.500 line:80%
the Lord locked him in the dark prison

00:20:03.020 --> 00:20:05.050 line:80%
and set up

00:20:06.130 --> 00:20:07.980 line:80%
warning mechanisms.

00:20:09.050 --> 00:20:09.890 line:80%
Master,

00:20:10.180 --> 00:20:11.020 line:80%
Uncle Li,

00:20:11.660 --> 00:20:13.530 line:80%
Qian Xueshen almost replaced me.

00:20:13.700 --> 00:20:14.780 line:80%
Zhao and Chang

00:20:14.780 --> 00:20:16.290 line:80%
also worried about the demon sect

00:20:16.500 --> 00:20:18.416 line:80%
might have switched someone else,

00:20:18.427 --> 00:20:19.780 line:80%
so they entered the secret prison

00:20:19.810 --> 00:20:21.460 line:80%
to find the antidote to the Body Shift.

00:20:21.530 --> 00:20:22.370 line:80%
Xingjia,

00:20:22.460 --> 00:20:24.500 line:80%
did you witness Qian Xueshen

00:20:24.500 --> 00:20:26.130 line:80%
using the Body Shift?

00:20:26.420 --> 00:20:27.260 line:80%
I...

00:20:30.780 --> 00:20:31.810 line:80%
When I woke up,

00:20:32.660 --> 00:20:33.660 line:80%
he had been taken away.

00:20:33.890 --> 00:20:35.420 line:80%
You didn't see it;

00:20:35.940 --> 00:20:37.850 line:80%
that's just their side of the story.

00:20:38.260 --> 00:20:39.700 line:80%
Demon sect members are cunning.

00:20:40.090 --> 00:20:41.220 line:80%
We can't believe it blindly.

00:20:42.420 --> 00:20:43.610 line:80%
Take him away.

00:20:43.660 --> 00:20:44.570 line:80%
Keep him imprisoned.

00:20:45.020 --> 00:20:46.300 line:80%
- Yes.
- Wait.

00:20:54.460 --> 00:20:55.570 line:80%
Among those present,

00:20:56.050 --> 00:20:57.260 line:80%
aside from Qian Xueshen,

00:21:00.050 --> 00:21:01.740 line:80%
there is another one
of the demonic sect.

00:21:05.020 --> 00:21:05.860 line:80%
Who?

00:21:13.130 --> 00:21:14.130 line:80%
Ning.

00:21:15.500 --> 00:21:17.260 line:80%
Does the Jiuzhou Archive
of the demonic sect

00:21:17.890 --> 00:21:20.130 line:80%
really hold books as vast as the sea?

00:21:22.570 --> 00:21:23.410 line:80%
Zhao,

00:21:23.940 --> 00:21:24.940 line:80%
what are you saying?

00:21:25.420 --> 00:21:27.370 line:80%
You schemed to infiltrate Qingque Sect

00:21:28.050 --> 00:21:29.290 line:80%
just to gain my trust.

00:21:30.020 --> 00:21:31.890 line:80%
Then you helped Ms. Luo come here.

00:21:34.610 --> 00:21:36.090 line:80%
During the memorial chaos,

00:21:36.453 --> 00:21:37.599 line:80%
you left Wu Gang and Wu Xiong

00:21:37.610 --> 00:21:38.796 line:80%
to coordinate inside the sect.

00:21:39.700 --> 00:21:41.640 line:80%
You even killed the guards
at Thousandfold Cliff,

00:21:41.890 --> 00:21:43.130 line:80%
helping the demon sect attack,

00:21:46.180 --> 00:21:48.290 line:80%
causing Master to be injured

00:21:48.370 --> 00:21:49.570 line:80%
and go into seclusion,

00:21:50.090 --> 00:21:51.700 line:80%
so your replacement plan

00:21:52.050 --> 00:21:53.420 line:80%
would succeed without fail.

00:21:55.700 --> 00:21:56.540 line:80%
Chang Ning,

00:21:57.460 --> 00:21:58.660 line:80%
you are a demon sect spy!

00:21:58.700 --> 00:21:59.980 line:80%
Seize this spy!

00:22:02.610 --> 00:22:03.450 line:80%
Stop!

00:22:12.330 --> 00:22:13.180 line:80%
- Zhao!
- Zhao!

00:22:13.180 --> 00:22:14.020 line:80%
Dalou!

00:22:14.130 --> 00:22:15.570 line:80%
Cai Zhao, are you mad?

00:22:15.740 --> 00:22:17.050 line:80%
If I kill the wrong person today,

00:22:17.850 --> 00:22:19.220 line:80%
I'll give my life to repay his.

00:22:19.420 --> 00:22:20.260 line:80%
You...

00:23:05.370 --> 00:23:06.970 line:80%
Look, Dalou has changed.

00:23:15.420 --> 00:23:16.740 line:80%
So, there really is a Body Shift.

00:23:19.050 --> 00:23:20.610 line:80%
Then who is this person?

00:23:21.940 --> 00:23:23.020 line:80%
Where is the real Dalou?

00:23:25.090 --> 00:23:25.930 line:80%
When the person dies,

00:23:26.890 --> 00:23:27.980 line:80%
the Body Shift ends.

00:23:28.570 --> 00:23:30.290 line:80%
This is the spy impersonating Dalou.

00:23:31.500 --> 00:23:32.610 line:80%
The real Dalou

00:23:33.370 --> 00:23:35.090 line:80%
is hidden somewhere unknown.

00:23:36.620 --> 00:23:37.470 line:80%
I don't know.

00:23:37.500 --> 00:23:38.420 line:80%
I know nothing.

00:23:39.890 --> 00:23:41.180 line:80%
The only person present

00:23:41.660 --> 00:23:43.780 line:80%
who knows where Dalou is

00:23:44.610 --> 00:23:45.610 line:80%
is Master.

00:23:46.700 --> 00:23:47.850 line:80%
Because you are also fake.

00:23:48.020 --> 00:23:48.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:23:52.460 --> 00:23:53.850 line:80%
for your aunt's sake,

00:23:54.180 --> 00:23:55.810 line:80%
your mischief is normally forgiven,

00:23:56.090 --> 00:23:58.090 line:80%
but accusations can't be made randomly.

00:23:58.700 --> 00:23:59.540 line:80%
Dear,

00:24:00.050 --> 00:24:01.650 line:80%
Zhao was deceived

00:24:01.980 --> 00:24:03.660 line:80%
by the demon sect.

00:24:04.180 --> 00:24:06.500 line:80%
She's inexperienced and naive.

00:24:06.780 --> 00:24:08.460 line:80%
She's just used without realizing it.

00:24:09.420 --> 00:24:10.370 line:80%
Qian Xueshen,

00:24:10.780 --> 00:24:12.180 line:80%
you did the job. Say it.

00:24:14.610 --> 00:24:15.450 line:80%
I...

00:24:17.660 --> 00:24:18.740 line:80%
The one I swapped

00:24:19.330 --> 00:24:20.170 line:80%
was poisoned

00:24:20.890 --> 00:24:22.090 line:80%
and highly skilled.

00:24:23.180 --> 00:24:24.020 line:80%
That's him.

00:24:28.780 --> 00:24:29.780 line:80%
Demon sect members

00:24:30.180 --> 00:24:31.660 line:80%
swapped a few of our own

00:24:32.050 --> 00:24:33.850 line:80%
to create distrust among us.

00:24:34.290 --> 00:24:35.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:35.500 --> 00:24:37.290 line:80%
you fell for their trick.

00:24:38.130 --> 00:24:38.970 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:39.020 --> 00:24:40.610 line:80%
your master usually dotes on you.

00:24:41.330 --> 00:24:43.260 line:80%
How could you frame him

00:24:43.290 --> 00:24:44.260 line:80%
with demon sect spies?

00:24:44.660 --> 00:24:45.500 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:24:46.180 --> 00:24:48.700 line:80%
Master always used
his injuries as an excuse,

00:24:49.020 --> 00:24:50.740 line:80%
ignoring years of marital affection,

00:24:51.460 --> 00:24:52.810 line:80%
and avoided you,

00:24:53.050 --> 00:24:54.290 line:80%
yet you doubted him not at all?

00:25:01.290 --> 00:25:02.850 line:80%
Our marital bond

00:25:03.420 --> 00:25:05.500 line:80%
is not for juniors to meddle in.

00:25:05.940 --> 00:25:08.500 line:80%
Wenxun, Cai Zhao is obstinate.
Seize her.

00:25:26.660 --> 00:25:27.900 line:80%
- Father!
- Yunke!

00:25:27.900 --> 00:25:28.750 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:25:28.750 --> 00:25:29.600 line:80%
Li Wenxun!

00:25:30.460 --> 00:25:31.300 line:80%
Wenxun,

00:25:31.940 --> 00:25:33.370 line:80%
can you now prove it?

00:25:38.260 --> 00:25:39.100 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:25:39.276 --> 00:25:40.260 line:80%
appearances can be faked,

00:25:40.780 --> 00:25:42.020 line:80%
but martial skills can't.

00:25:44.290 --> 00:25:45.660 line:80%
As everyone saw,

00:25:46.130 --> 00:25:47.050 line:80%
the Lord indeed used

00:25:47.370 --> 00:25:48.780 line:80%
our mindful way.

00:25:49.500 --> 00:25:50.810 line:80%
We can't believe just one account.

00:25:52.130 --> 00:25:52.980 line:80%
I've verified

00:25:53.330 --> 00:25:54.170 line:80%
that the Body Shift

00:25:54.290 --> 00:25:55.130 line:80%
threatens the sect.

00:25:55.610 --> 00:25:56.676 line:80%
Since you don't believe me,

00:25:57.050 --> 00:25:58.050 line:80%
do as you will

00:25:58.980 --> 00:25:59.850 line:80%
from now on.

00:26:00.460 --> 00:26:01.400 line:80%
I'm leaving immediately.

00:26:02.020 --> 00:26:03.026 line:80%
It's none of my business.

00:26:05.810 --> 00:26:06.650 line:80%
Let's go.

00:26:06.870 --> 00:26:07.710 line:80%
Wenxun,

00:26:07.740 --> 00:26:08.580 line:80%
stop her.

00:26:08.740 --> 00:26:10.090 line:80%
She can't take Qian Xueshen away.

00:26:17.850 --> 00:26:18.690 line:80%
Wenxun.

00:26:19.180 --> 00:26:21.090 line:80%
What's happening here?

00:26:21.940 --> 00:26:22.780 line:80%
Yunke,

00:26:23.500 --> 00:26:25.370 line:80%
as the Lord of Qingque Sect,

00:26:25.370 --> 00:26:26.810 line:80%
why are you opposing juniors?

00:26:27.130 --> 00:26:28.180 line:80%
If you hurt Zhao

00:26:28.180 --> 00:26:29.020 line:80%
by accident,

00:26:29.050 --> 00:26:30.130 line:80%
what should we do?

00:26:30.780 --> 00:26:31.620 line:80%
Shijun,

00:26:31.850 --> 00:26:32.810 line:80%
you don't know.

00:26:33.260 --> 00:26:35.370 line:80%
Qian Xueshen is from Qianmian Sect.

00:26:35.890 --> 00:26:37.180 line:80%
If he enters Jianghu,

00:26:37.290 --> 00:26:38.420 line:80%
he will cause great trouble.

00:26:38.940 --> 00:26:40.180 line:80%
You need not interfere.

00:26:41.050 --> 00:26:41.890 line:80%
That won't do.

00:26:42.180 --> 00:26:44.570 line:80%
Our members have always been upright.

00:26:45.090 --> 00:26:46.260 line:80%
If the righteous qi

00:26:46.500 --> 00:26:47.850 line:80%
in my dantian

00:26:47.850 --> 00:26:48.810 line:80%
is released,

00:26:49.220 --> 00:26:50.060 line:80%
it will burst out.

00:26:50.660 --> 00:26:52.180 line:80%
We can't suppress it.

00:26:52.740 --> 00:26:53.740 line:80%
So,

00:26:53.740 --> 00:26:54.610 line:80%
I must intervene.

00:26:54.610 --> 00:26:55.450 line:80%
Let's go.

00:26:57.940 --> 00:26:59.030 line:80%
Wenxun, stop them!

00:26:59.050 --> 00:26:59.940 line:80%
They can't leave!

00:27:00.570 --> 00:27:01.420 line:80%
They won't.

00:27:01.420 --> 00:27:02.260 line:80%
They won't leave.

00:27:02.780 --> 00:27:05.090 line:80%
The mountains are filled with my men.

00:27:05.570 --> 00:27:07.980 line:80%
I just worry about you.

00:27:08.330 --> 00:27:10.090 line:80%
I heard you were attacked

00:27:10.220 --> 00:27:11.500 line:80%
and badly injured.

00:27:12.220 --> 00:27:13.060 line:80%
I'm so worried.

00:27:13.130 --> 00:27:15.850 line:80%
You must take care of your health now.

00:27:33.610 --> 00:27:35.256 line:80%
We're really going
to the snow mountains?

00:27:35.570 --> 00:27:36.410 line:80%
If you stay,

00:27:36.780 --> 00:27:37.780 line:80%
you'll surely die.

00:27:38.330 --> 00:27:39.170 line:80%
Come with me.

00:27:39.326 --> 00:27:40.919 line:80%
Maybe there's still a chance to survive.

00:27:43.740 --> 00:27:44.580 line:80%
Zhao.

00:27:47.620 --> 00:27:48.470 line:80%
Yuzhi?

00:27:48.500 --> 00:27:49.810 line:80%
The Body Shift is now public.

00:27:49.970 --> 00:27:51.500 line:80%
The Guangtian Sect will guard strictly.

00:27:51.500 --> 00:27:52.863 line:80%
The impostor dares not act rashly.

00:27:52.980 --> 00:27:53.820 line:80%
In time,

00:27:53.890 --> 00:27:55.530 line:80%
Lord Cai and Lord Zhou will arrive.

00:27:55.700 --> 00:27:57.530 line:80%
Once the truth is out,
Master will be found.

00:27:57.700 --> 00:27:58.540 line:80%
You don't have to go.

00:28:02.570 --> 00:28:03.743 line:80%
The Body Shift has no flaw.

00:28:03.754 --> 00:28:05.689 line:80%
The impostor even knows
our sect's mindful ways.

00:28:05.700 --> 00:28:06.740 line:80%
Should I let my father

00:28:07.030 --> 00:28:08.420 line:80%
commit a grave injustice to kill him

00:28:08.740 --> 00:28:09.690 line:80%
to verify his identity?

00:28:11.530 --> 00:28:12.370 line:80%
No.

00:28:12.460 --> 00:28:13.890 line:80%
He is the Lord of the top sect.

00:28:14.610 --> 00:28:16.420 line:80%
If we can't expose him publicly,

00:28:16.530 --> 00:28:17.690 line:80%
how can we break the deadlock?

00:28:17.940 --> 00:28:18.736 line:80%
Waiting another day

00:28:18.747 --> 00:28:20.279 line:80%
means another day of danger for Master.

00:28:20.290 --> 00:28:22.530 line:80%
Rather than wait in fear and doubt,

00:28:22.700 --> 00:28:24.370 line:80%
we should go to retrieve the saliva.

00:28:24.700 --> 00:28:25.833 line:80%
Maybe there's still a chance.

00:28:26.370 --> 00:28:27.850 line:80%
The horses and luggage are ready.

00:28:28.610 --> 00:28:29.450 line:80%
Take care, Zhao.

00:28:31.090 --> 00:28:31.930 line:80%
Zhao!

00:28:33.780 --> 00:28:35.300 line:80%
- Xiaolan?
- Zhao,

00:28:35.980 --> 00:28:38.050 line:80%
with my poor skills, I can't help much.

00:28:38.220 --> 00:28:40.180 line:80%
Here's some money I've saved,

00:28:40.180 --> 00:28:41.333 line:80%
always useful when traveling.

00:28:41.940 --> 00:28:43.420 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:28:44.290 --> 00:28:45.130 line:80%
don't worry.

00:28:45.180 --> 00:28:46.850 line:80%
Yuzhi has prepared the money.

00:28:48.090 --> 00:28:49.280 line:80%
No, it's different.

00:28:49.850 --> 00:28:51.050 line:80%
Zhao, don't worry.

00:28:51.130 --> 00:28:51.970 line:80%
Take it.

00:28:52.980 --> 00:28:54.090 line:80%
Then I'll take it.

00:28:54.780 --> 00:28:56.090 line:80%
I'll definitely practice hard

00:28:56.530 --> 00:28:58.180 line:80%
and stay with Yuzhi to guard here,

00:28:58.420 --> 00:28:59.380 line:80%
waiting for your return.

00:28:59.700 --> 00:29:00.540 line:80%
Wait for me.

00:29:14.290 --> 00:29:15.823 line:80%
The Lord has gone into seclusion again.

00:29:16.180 --> 00:29:18.780 line:80%
Lord Song sealed
the iron chain mechanisms.

00:29:19.330 --> 00:29:22.220 line:80%
No one may enter or leave now.

00:29:22.850 --> 00:29:23.690 line:80%
Nanny Mao,

00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:25.700 line:80%
could it be

00:29:26.260 --> 00:29:27.290 line:80%
that he's indeed fake?

00:29:31.980 --> 00:29:34.940 line:80%
Double Lotus Palace is closed
starting today.

00:29:35.700 --> 00:29:36.780 line:80%
All we can do

00:29:38.740 --> 00:29:40.290 line:80%
is wait for the result.

00:29:41.020 --> 00:29:41.860 line:80%
Where's Cai Zhao?

00:29:43.260 --> 00:29:44.740 line:80%
She left.

00:30:31.780 --> 00:30:33.020 line:80%
Miss Cai.

00:30:33.460 --> 00:30:35.090 line:80%
- Nature calls.
- Nature calls.

00:30:38.460 --> 00:30:39.780 line:80%
I need to release myself.

00:30:42.050 --> 00:30:42.890 line:80%
My stomach...

00:30:43.220 --> 00:30:44.130 line:80%
You can't escape.

00:30:47.370 --> 00:30:48.210 line:80%
I'm not running.

00:30:56.330 --> 00:30:57.290 line:80%
Ghost!

00:30:57.370 --> 00:30:58.210 line:80%
Ghost!

00:30:59.940 --> 00:31:00.780 line:80%
A seductive ghost!

00:31:02.020 --> 00:31:02.860 line:80%
A seductive ghost!

00:31:12.890 --> 00:31:13.980 line:80%
Seductive...

00:31:15.573 --> 00:31:16.653 line:80%
Where's the seductive ghost?

00:31:17.570 --> 00:31:18.570 line:80%
It was just here.

00:31:19.850 --> 00:31:20.690 line:80%
Seductive ghost!

00:31:29.980 --> 00:31:30.820 line:80%
Zhao.

00:31:32.530 --> 00:31:34.220 line:80%
Does this ghost know you?

00:31:38.290 --> 00:31:39.290 line:80%
May I ask...

00:31:39.330 --> 00:31:40.170 line:80%
My name is

00:31:40.570 --> 00:31:41.530 line:80%
Mu Qingyan.

00:31:42.850 --> 00:31:44.020 line:80%
I've been waiting here

00:31:44.220 --> 00:31:45.810 line:80%
for you for a day and a night.

00:31:47.850 --> 00:31:49.260 line:80%
Trying to scare me?

00:32:19.850 --> 00:32:20.780 line:80%
(Chang Ning?)

00:32:20.780 --> 00:32:22.460 line:80%
(Mu Qingyan, Young Master of Li Sect)

00:32:31.610 --> 00:32:32.450 line:80%
Zhao,

00:32:33.420 --> 00:32:34.473 line:80%
what do you mean by this?

00:32:34.746 --> 00:32:36.846 line:80%
Luoying Valley and the demon sect
are sworn enemies,

00:32:36.980 --> 00:32:38.420 line:80%
let alone their young master.

00:33:12.670 --> 00:33:13.530 line:80%
Go!

00:33:13.530 --> 00:33:15.610 line:80%
If Mr. Qian doesn't take my antidote,

00:33:15.740 --> 00:33:16.580 line:80%
he will die suddenly

00:33:16.810 --> 00:33:18.220 line:80%
by tonight.

00:33:21.500 --> 00:33:22.340 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:33:22.740 --> 00:33:23.780 line:80%
what exactly do you want?

00:33:26.330 --> 00:33:27.370 line:80%
The wonton is ready

00:33:28.940 --> 00:33:30.090 line:80%
to go into the pot.

00:33:48.660 --> 00:33:49.570 line:80%
What antidote?

00:33:50.260 --> 00:33:51.220 line:80%
Back in the dungeon,

00:33:51.220 --> 00:33:53.530 line:80%
I accidentally fed him
a Chasing Pill,

00:33:54.130 --> 00:33:56.610 line:80%
also called a Seizing Pill.

00:33:56.700 --> 00:33:58.330 line:80%
You set a trap in the dungeon?

00:33:59.890 --> 00:34:01.050 line:80%
Didn't you plot against me

00:34:01.050 --> 00:34:01.980 line:80%
in the dungeon?

00:34:03.980 --> 00:34:04.850 line:80%
No one will believe

00:34:04.850 --> 00:34:06.460 line:80%
the Lord of the top sect is fake.

00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:08.700 line:80%
No one will believe you.

00:34:13.580 --> 00:34:14.450 line:80%
I have a plan.

00:34:15.580 --> 00:34:16.420 line:80%
I'll do it with you.

00:34:18.450 --> 00:34:19.290 line:80%
We're even.

00:34:20.410 --> 00:34:21.250 line:80%
Give me the antidote.

00:34:21.580 --> 00:34:22.420 line:80%
No rush.

00:34:23.410 --> 00:34:24.930 line:80%
Try this pickled bamboo shoots first.

00:34:25.260 --> 00:34:26.260 line:80%
Uncle Chang taught me.

00:34:26.700 --> 00:34:27.540 line:80%
Luzhou style.

00:34:27.850 --> 00:34:28.810 line:80%
Perfect

00:34:28.850 --> 00:34:29.690 line:80%
with wonton.

00:34:29.850 --> 00:34:31.163 line:80%
Uncle Chang has always hated evil

00:34:31.620 --> 00:34:33.370 line:80%
and never aligned with the demon sect.

00:34:34.060 --> 00:34:34.900 line:80%
I don't understand

00:34:35.580 --> 00:34:36.540 line:80%
why he'd help you.

00:34:37.660 --> 00:34:38.500 line:80%
Probably

00:34:39.850 --> 00:34:41.220 line:80%
because I'm a good person.

00:34:42.780 --> 00:34:44.010 line:80%
Before, in Dusk Palace,

00:34:44.220 --> 00:34:45.410 line:80%
you put me in great danger,

00:34:45.890 --> 00:34:47.223 line:80%
yet I still treated you to wonton.

00:34:47.410 --> 00:34:48.803 line:80%
Doesn't that make me a good person?

00:34:50.010 --> 00:34:50.850 line:80%
Enough.

00:34:51.450 --> 00:34:52.580 line:80%
I know you'll escape.

00:34:52.780 --> 00:34:54.100 line:80%
As the Young Master of Li Sect,

00:34:54.930 --> 00:34:56.850 line:80%
my father was close to Mr. Chang.

00:34:57.700 --> 00:34:58.540 line:80%
Back then,

00:34:58.660 --> 00:35:01.490 line:80%
Mr. Chang got lost
while attacking Youming Path

00:35:02.220 --> 00:35:03.370 line:80%
with the Six Sects.

00:35:03.810 --> 00:35:05.810 line:80%
He ran into my father raising a Peng.

00:35:06.410 --> 00:35:07.783 line:80%
My father saw him severely injured,

00:35:07.930 --> 00:35:08.890 line:80%
so he healed him

00:35:08.930 --> 00:35:10.140 line:80%
and showed him a way out.

00:35:10.780 --> 00:35:11.850 line:80%
Since then, Mr. Chang

00:35:11.850 --> 00:35:13.780 line:80%
has remembered my father's kindness

00:35:14.410 --> 00:35:15.490 line:80%
and promised

00:35:16.100 --> 00:35:17.330 line:80%
that if I were ever in danger,

00:35:18.100 --> 00:35:19.330 line:80%
he'd protect me.

00:35:23.810 --> 00:35:25.290 line:80%
Uncle Chang has always been grateful.

00:35:26.660 --> 00:35:28.220 line:80%
That's indeed something he'd do.

00:35:30.010 --> 00:35:30.850 line:80%
A year ago,

00:35:31.680 --> 00:35:33.553 line:80%
Nie Zhe wiped out
the remnants of the Mu clan,

00:35:33.890 --> 00:35:35.890 line:80%
claiming he killed the Young Master.

00:35:36.140 --> 00:35:37.220 line:80%
Was the poison on you

00:35:38.410 --> 00:35:39.700 line:80%
left then?

00:35:39.850 --> 00:35:41.643 line:80%
The Li Sect has always belonged
to my family.

00:35:42.450 --> 00:35:43.740 line:80%
After Nie Hengcheng died,

00:35:44.620 --> 00:35:45.740 line:80%
Nie Zhe wanted to take over,

00:35:46.100 --> 00:35:47.150 line:80%
so he couldn't tolerate me.

00:35:47.660 --> 00:35:48.850 line:80%
He seriously injured me.

00:35:55.410 --> 00:35:56.700 line:80%
Nie Zhe practiced the Wudu Palm.

00:35:57.330 --> 00:35:58.170 line:80%
I couldn't beat him.

00:35:58.170 --> 00:36:00.140 line:80%
(Nie Zhe, Chief of Li Sect)

00:36:03.060 --> 00:36:03.900 line:80%
Then,

00:36:04.140 --> 00:36:05.490 line:80%
I escaped to Chang Fort.

00:36:33.700 --> 00:36:34.540 line:80%
Here.

00:36:56.780 --> 00:36:57.930 line:80%
He kept his promise

00:36:58.450 --> 00:36:59.576 line:80%
and protected me to the end.

00:37:01.370 --> 00:37:03.060 line:80%
The Chang Fort saved my life.

00:37:04.290 --> 00:37:05.580 line:80%
When I return to Li Sect,

00:37:06.060 --> 00:37:07.220 line:80%
I'll strip Nie Zhe

00:37:08.140 --> 00:37:09.580 line:80%
and the Demonic Camp

00:37:11.060 --> 00:37:12.220 line:80%
to the bones.

00:37:14.700 --> 00:37:15.540 line:80%
Enough.

00:37:16.060 --> 00:37:17.450 line:80%
That's your demon sect business.

00:37:18.010 --> 00:37:18.890 line:80%
Give me the antidote.

00:37:19.540 --> 00:37:20.380 line:80%
From now on,

00:37:20.580 --> 00:37:21.700 line:80%
we go

00:37:22.140 --> 00:37:23.220 line:80%
our separate ways.

00:37:23.540 --> 00:37:24.580 line:80%
Zhao, you want

00:37:25.290 --> 00:37:26.370 line:80%
to cut ties with me?

00:37:26.850 --> 00:37:28.180 line:80%
Luoying Valley isn't just mine.

00:37:28.740 --> 00:37:29.613 line:80%
It belongs to my aunt,

00:37:29.780 --> 00:37:31.310 line:80%
my father, my mother,

00:37:31.330 --> 00:37:32.740 line:80%
and countless valley residents.

00:37:33.410 --> 00:37:34.589 line:80%
I can't selfishly

00:37:34.600 --> 00:37:35.930 line:80%
let the whole valley be accused

00:37:35.930 --> 00:37:37.330 line:80%
of colluding with the demon sect.

00:37:37.700 --> 00:37:38.740 line:80%
Collude all you want.

00:37:39.930 --> 00:37:41.290 line:80%
Just bring the entire valley over

00:37:41.740 --> 00:37:42.740 line:80%
if you like.

00:37:43.290 --> 00:37:44.290 line:80%
Like Qianmian Sect?

00:37:44.850 --> 00:37:46.410 line:80%
Ending up with total destruction?

00:37:49.606 --> 00:37:51.272 line:80%
Since you refuse
to give me the antidote,

00:37:53.620 --> 00:37:55.110 line:80%
if something happens to Qian Xueshen,

00:37:55.370 --> 00:37:56.260 line:80%
it's his fate.

00:38:01.260 --> 00:38:02.100 line:80%
Let's go.

00:38:02.580 --> 00:38:03.546 line:80%
Do we have the antidote?

00:38:07.640 --> 00:38:08.580 line:80%
Take three pills a day

00:38:08.820 --> 00:38:09.900 line:80%
for three consecutive days.

00:38:25.740 --> 00:38:26.780 line:80%
The snow mountains are

00:38:26.780 --> 00:38:28.013 line:80%
at least a thousand miles away.

00:38:28.330 --> 00:38:29.740 line:80%
Even riding fast,

00:38:29.751 --> 00:38:30.810 line:80%
without eating or drinking,

00:38:30.850 --> 00:38:32.060 line:80%
it'll take dozens of days.

00:38:32.370 --> 00:38:33.580 line:80%
Better take my Golden Peng.

00:38:33.946 --> 00:38:35.010 line:80%
You'll arrive in two days.

00:38:35.060 --> 00:38:36.280 line:80%
Ride a bird?

00:38:36.620 --> 00:38:37.890 line:80%
What if we fall?

00:38:38.450 --> 00:38:39.656 line:80%
This is an ancient Golden Peng.

00:38:41.540 --> 00:38:43.580 line:80%
With all this threatening and bribing,

00:38:44.290 --> 00:38:45.130 line:80%
what do you want?

00:38:45.450 --> 00:38:46.396 line:80%
I'm worried about you.

00:38:46.930 --> 00:38:48.060 line:80%
I want to go with you.

00:38:48.260 --> 00:38:49.620 line:80%
- No.
- Then stay another night.

00:38:50.490 --> 00:38:51.890 line:80%
We've shared a room for so long.

00:38:52.540 --> 00:38:54.180 line:80%
Surely, there's some trust left.

00:38:54.410 --> 00:38:56.140 line:80%
You shared a room?

00:39:05.561 --> 00:39:16.221 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:39:34.981 --> 00:39:39.391 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:39:39.956 --> 00:39:44.571 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:39:44.911 --> 00:39:49.476 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:39:50.001 --> 00:39:54.301 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:39:57.246 --> 00:40:01.946 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:02.471 --> 00:40:06.761 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:40:07.421 --> 00:40:11.451 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:40:11.766 --> 00:40:16.891 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:40:17.466 --> 00:40:22.276 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:40:22.491 --> 00:40:26.661 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:40:27.386 --> 00:40:31.321 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:40:31.821 --> 00:40:37.096 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:40:59.826 --> 00:41:04.956 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:41:05.321 --> 00:41:09.691 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:41:09.956 --> 00:41:14.086 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:41:14.271 --> 00:41:19.846 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪